Title: To Gilneas
Description:
$n, we've received word of an offensive occurring soon in Gilneas. 

We have been working with the Alliance to return Gilneas to the Gilneans. Unfortunately, the Scarlet Crusade have taken up residence in the city.

We wish to provide assistance in purging the Scarlet's and return the Gilneans lands to them. 

Lilian and I want you to join us in this operation.
ObjectivesText: Travel to Gilneas in Eastern Kingdoms to assist with retaking Gilneas City for the Gilneans.

Objectives.Text: Talk to Tess to go to Gilneas
